{"word":"ἀποτροπή","slug":"ἀποτροπή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποτροπή</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀποτρέπω'><el>ἀποτρέπω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a turning away, averting</i>, <el>κακῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a hindering, prevention</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(from <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>) <i>desertion of one's party</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}